{"tid":1902716,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎智英次仔茶餐廳二手凍檸茶奉客　認錯道歉","createTime":"2020-02-28T13:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T18:23:11.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8947e2fa4a61d1355a0c0ef5e8493100ed8c107b","tid":1902716,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200228/photo/bkn-20200228195646795-0228_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200228200912\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200228%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200228195646795-0228_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200228200912&h=65a9780a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎耀恩(左圖)為黎智英(右圖)的次子。<br />\n<br />\n在新冠肺炎之下，口水可以播毒，而壹傳媒黎智英次子黎耀恩在中環開設的茶餐廳「四季常餐」，竟將客人飲過的凍檸茶，再給另一位客人飲，令人噁心。「四季常餐」認錯，向客人致歉。<br />\n有客人前日(26日)下午1時到威靈頓街的「四季常餐」，叫了凍檸茶走甜，但飲過發現「勁甜」，於是叫侍應換過另一杯。客人發現侍應拿走該杯凍檸茶後，放入雪櫃，之後有侍應將放在雪櫃的該杯凍檸茶轉給另一顧客飲用。該客人隨即質問侍應：「依家咁嘅時勢，嗰杯嘢我飲過㗎，有無搞錯啊你哋！」侍應辯稱：「我哋收番嗰杯嘢，點知你飲過啫？」客人反問：「我無飲過又點知呢杯嘢唔係走甜啊？」<br />\n「四季常餐」其後在Facebook回應說，經過管理層了解事件及翻看CCTV，認為要為該等嚴重失誤負上全責，更稱該種失誤是完全不能接受，向客人及香港市民致歉。管理層正在認真處理事情，並作相對措施，如改善出餐流程和加強同事的服務及培訓，防止再有類似事情發生。「四季常餐」又多謝該位客人提醒，正嘗試聯絡及補償，希望得到其回覆，並再次道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200228/photo/bkn-20200228195646795-0228_00822_001_02p.jpg?20200228200912\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200228%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200228195646795-0228_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20200228200912&h=3db7d122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「四季常餐」在Fb就事件認錯，向客人致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200228/mobile/bkn-20200228195646795-0228_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200228%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200228195646795-0228_00822_001.html&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJGbkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=da3be953\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200228/mobile/bkn-20200228195646795-0228_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f0270ce66e39045fc02064f5588819957c53325e","tid":1902716,"uid":220451,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:30:29.000Z","msg":"道左歉 罷食 完"},{"pid":"a88b858ae046a169558a702f92f9f5077ac13d4c","tid":1902716,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:31:25.000Z","msg":"佢老婆係曾美華"},{"pid":"05c1688edaf7643c0d57d643be33431df1c07414","tid":1902716,"uid":6532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:32:20.000Z","msg":"好撚大獲，道歉都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e9790bfcb6baa8b1ed7e44b0cd69deac74199e","tid":1902716,"uid":188411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"黃藍是政見，罷食是良知"},{"pid":"06abc8d7ce699e7392c4c27272376cc80cfcb87c","tid":1902716,"uid":291750,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:33:59.000Z","msg":"呢個真係好令人擔心，即使係黃店，我都應該唔會幫襯！"},{"pid":"aba56a80a9c2d7c28c67f03621dd71a16d5a76f6","tid":1902716,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:34:48.000Z","msg":"明顯俾人陷害啦, 岩岩支共搞完肥佬黎, 又再搞埋佢個仔<br />\n大家唔好中計啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a87d3836fecdf5dea244df7227dbd0fa7f6b4f","tid":1902716,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:34:49.000Z","msg":"勁仆街"},{"pid":"48a4bd0be9d3d81bfb6a2d989a91378617fc6d5d","tid":1902716,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:36:00.000Z","msg":"P牌仔出曬黎開工~<br />\n真係支共次次都係咁<br />\n比少少技術好唔好"},{"pid":"04cb4c275b9b4254cb69c3f2eeebfad4457c43f0","tid":1902716,"uid":83228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:36:34.000Z","msg":"成日班p係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993bcc23169f794e1f5e42850acce4a6ff0eb506","tid":1902716,"uid